ValueSet: LinkRelationVS
Id: syndication-link-relation
Title: "Syndication Link Relation"
Description: """
The Atom `<link rel>` values that have defined meaning inside a
terminology syndication entry. Other IANA-registered values MAY be
used but have no syndication-specific semantics.
"""
* ^url = "https://ontoserver.csiro.au/syndication/ValueSet/syndication-link-relation"
* http://hl7.org/fhir/iana-link-relations#alternate "alternate"
* http://hl7.org/fhir/iana-link-relations#related "related"
* http://hl7.org/fhir/iana-link-relations#self "self"
